name: NubDog
description: $NubDog is the crypto equivalent of that one dog meme that just gets the culture - think "distracted boyfriend" but with a dog that's got its eye on the moon instead of another dog. It's the kind of memecoin where the community is as wild as a pack of dogs at a barbecue, with memes flying around faster than a dog chasing its tail. The vibe? It's like the OG cat memes of the internet - quirky, relatable, and with an edge of absurdity that keeps you laughing while you're watching your investment.
